Usage: define_glitch_holding_resistance [-help]
                                        [-glitch_type {both vl vh vlu vho vl_vh vlu_vho}]
                                        [-instance_pin <string>]
                                        [-lib_pin <string>] -value <float>
                                        [-views <string>]

-help                      # Prints out the command usage
-glitch_type {both vl vh vlu vho vl_vh vlu_vho}
                           # specifies the glitch type for rHold application (enum, optional)
-instance_pin <string>     # specify list of instance pin names
                           # (list, optional)
-lib_pin <string>          # specify list of library pin names (list, optional)
-value <float>             # specify the value in ohms of the holding
                           # resistance to be used by glitch analysis
                           # (float, required)
-views <string>            # specify the list of view names (list, optional)